                            <comment id="12940612" author="djencks" created="Mon, 29 Dec 2008 07:58:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;rev 729835 adds consistency checks to Valve and removes the unbalanced decrement.  IMO this should be reviewed by a more knowledgeable developer before closing... Hiram can you take a look or suggest someone who could?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12940608" author="chirino" created="Fri, 2 Jan 2009 18:05:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks good.  Perhaps we should change those consistency checks to assert calls so that users can avoid doing them in production since they are being done in synchronized blocks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
